<i> [Adam] She's literally not</i>
<i>  inside the house.</i>

01:25.119 --> 01:27.086
<i>  The house looks</i>
<i>  so non-assuming.</i>

01:27.088 --> 01:30.022
<i> [Amy] But we've learned</i>
<i>  our lesson on that before.</i>

01:31.225 --> 01:33.158
-[Adam] Leanne?
-[Leanne] Yes?

01:33.160 --> 01:34.927
-Hey, Leanne.
-[Leanne] Hi! Hello.

