01:57.818 --> 01:59.118
Yeah.

02:00.354 --> 02:02.287
Now, when was
this house built?

02:02.289 --> 02:05.691
-[Leanne] I do believe
it was 1946.
-[Amy] Okay.

02:05.693 --> 02:08.260
-[Amy] And you bought it
in 2008? Okay.
-[Leanne] Yep.

02:08.262 --> 02:10.496
[Leanne] I met my husband
and I moved to Westchester.

02:11.465 --> 02:14.166
Um, my mum, she's elderly.
