07:24.878 --> 07:26.178
[Leanne] I am, but I'm not.

07:26.180 --> 07:28.947
My brother... My older brother
died when he was three.

07:28.949 --> 07:31.149
-Oh, geez.
-[Adam] Oh, I'm sorry. Okay.

07:31.151 --> 07:33.251
So, and then, I was born
seven years later.

07:33.253 --> 07:35.120
-[Amy] Mmm. Okay.
-[Adam] Okay.

07:35.122 --> 07:40.192
Is there anything that you do
that seems to either
make activity happen

07:40.194 --> 07:44.963
