-[Leanne] Just
be here, just...

07:44.965 --> 07:47.766
When I'm here,
it's like... they're like,
"Oh, there she is!"

07:47.768 --> 07:49.367
-[Amy] Mmm.
-[Leanne] We really need help.

07:49.369 --> 07:52.003
Well, you should be able
to come here
and visit your mom

07:52.005 --> 07:53.104
