07:53.106 --> 07:54.706
I'm scared all the time.

07:56.243 --> 07:58.276
-So, you're scared
all the time?
-[Leanne] Mm-hmm.

07:59.213 --> 08:01.880
-[Amy] Okay. No, it's okay.
